    • Method Detail

      • push

        public boolean push(PlayingCard inCard)
        push() attempst to push the card into the stack. This is only allowed if the card is the opposite color, and one value less then the top card, or if the initial deal is turned on
        Parameters:
        inCard - - the PlayingCard to be pushed to the TableStack;
        Returns:
        a boolean, true if the card was pushed into the stack, false if it was not.

      • canPush

        Parameters:
        inCard - - the PlayingCard to be tested
        Returns:
        boolean - true if it can be pushed into the stack, false if it cannot be
